# Node Guess Game with Docker

This is a simple number-guessing game built with Node.js and Docker. Follow the steps below to set it up and run it.

## Prerequisites

- Docker installed
- Node.js (version 16 or higher recommended)

## Project Structure

├── app.js
├── package.json
├── Dockerfile
└── public/
└── index.html


## Steps to Set Up and Run the Game

###  1. Clone the Repository

git clone https://github.com/mohameddhouib5/docker-project
cd docker-project

###  2. Build the Docker Image

docker build -t node-guess-game .

###  3. Run the Docker Container

docker run -p 3000:3000 node-guess-game

###  4. Access the Game Open your browser and visit:

http://localhost:3000

have fun 